{"tid":1240940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【公投】點解係遊行，而唔係直接集合包圍？","createTime":"2019-06-18T13:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T13:56:09.000Z","uid":2565,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"838e03093f77654338a82805b1d84869371f46ca","tid":1240940,"uid":2565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:52:22.000Z","msg":"如果遊行目標係展現群眾支持，咁遊咗兩次，乜柒都展現晒啦？依家事實話畀你聽，政府根本唔驚你慢慢行一日路拍下手再嗌口號。無人驚過你啊。直接集合包圍，一齊傳福音、唱聖詩，感動上帝保祐香港人咁唔係仲直接咩？仲要喺到等啲狗批准你遊行咁戇鳩？<br />\n<br />\n發夢見到周公咁樣同我玩學術討論，唔知點答佢好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />　繼續遊行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />　一齊求上帝保祐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩都唔投＝樓主收皮去瞓覺！"},{"pid":"5b02c573d29840969738693e8514b0f8c589795b","tid":1240940,"uid":188374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24933ea94946b24750d557c0df5f2d59c736b19","tid":1240940,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}